昨天三点左右  格温
Yesterday around 3:00, Gwen.

373
00:17:10,210 --> 00:17:12,630
注意到有哪个食物托盘里面放的不是吃的吗
Notice anything on the food trays that wasn't food?

374
00:17:12,640 --> 00:17:14,430
三点左右
Around 3:00?

375
00:17:14,840 --> 00:17:16,040
和往常一样
Just the usual --

376
00:17:16,620 --> 00:17:20,630
特百惠杯子  太阳眼镜  手机  一个避孕套
Tupperware, sunglasses, cellphones, a condom.

377
00:17:20,810 --> 00:17:22,370
四点左右  我找到了个玻璃假眼
Around 4:00, I found a glass eye.

378
00:17:22,550 --> 00:17:24,320
你有看到一个生物危害袋吗
You see a biohazard bag?

379
00:17:25,010 --> 00:17:27,450
上面有红圈的自封袋吗
The ziplock bag with the red circles?

380
00:17:27,450 --> 00:17:28,160
是的
Yeah.

381
00:17:29,650 --> 00:17:30,400
跟我来
C'mon.

382
00:17:35,090 --> 00:17:36,910
你可以动二尖瓣
You can move the mitral valve.

383
00:17:37,090 --> 00:17:39,070
谢谢你的直观教具
Thanks for the visual aid.

384
00:17:39,140 --> 00:17:40,850
你不能动二尖瓣
You can't move the mitral valve.

385
00:17:41,290 --> 00:17:43,730
如果土豆先生有个房间隔的鼻子
Now, if Mr. Potato Head had an atrial septal nose

386
00:17:43,730 --> 00:17:44,750
-和肥大性阻塞性心肌  -我相信
- and hypertrophic obstructive -- - I believe --

387
00:17:44,750 --> 00:17:48,840
-我相信二尖瓣附着异常可以... -停
- I believe the abnormal insertion of the mitral valve can be -- - Stop.

388
00:17:51,890 --> 00:17:52,720
跟我来
Follow me.

389
00:17:54,950 --> 00:17:58,800
我很确定昨天我在这里看到个生物危害袋
Pretty sure I saw a biohazard bag in here yesterday.

390
00:17:58,800 --> 00:18:00,320
你们很幸运现在过来找
You're lucky you came when you did.

391
