A biohazard bag for a coin purse?

399
00:18:21,180 --> 00:18:22,120
认真的吗
Really?

400
00:18:24,280 --> 00:18:26,500
最后  室间隔肌切开术
Finally, a septal myectomy

401
00:18:26,500 --> 00:18:27,940
可以切开流出道
will open the outflow tract,

402
00:18:27,950 --> 00:18:29,640
二尖瓣就可以被植入到
and the mitral valve can be re-implanted

403
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:31,560
一个更加正常的位置
into a more normal position.

404
00:18:31,820 --> 00:18:33,760
谢谢  这是我的想法
Thank you. That's my idea.

405
00:18:34,020 --> 00:18:35,860
