So, what was the point of this dog and pony show?

409
00:18:42,340 --> 00:18:44,810
因为看起来你很热衷于替我做医学决定
'Cause you seemed keen on making medical decisions for me.

410
00:18:44,810 --> 00:18:46,280
所以只是反抗而已
So just insubordination?

411
00:18:46,280 --> 00:18:48,790
反正我们最后还是得来找你
And we were probably gonna wind up coming to you anyway.

412
00:18:49,050 --> 00:18:51,400
一旦莫菲医生有一个想法  他都会坚持己见
Once Dr. Murphy gets an idea, he stays with it,

413
00:18:51,400 --> 00:18:53,140
无论别人说什么
regardless of what anyone says.

414
00:18:53,420 --> 00:18:54,780
是可以的
This can work.

415
00:18:54,790 --> 00:18:56,900
是的  是可以的
Yes, this can work.

416
00:18:57,000 --> 00:19:00,090
如果那孩子能活两小时  那真是个好主意
And it would be a great idea if the boy had two hours to live.

417
00:19:00,510 --> 00:19:03,720
害怕失败是不这么做的一个好理由吗
Is fear of failure a good reason not to do this?

418
00:19:06,010 --> 00:19:06,770
不
No.

419
00:19:07,860 --> 00:19:08,980
