But you know what is?

420
00:19:09,730 --> 00:19:12,870
他本可以多活几年的想法...
The thought that he might have a few more birthdays...

421
00:19:13,390 --> 00:19:15,150
或是交一个最好的朋友
or make a best friend.

422
00:19:16,500 --> 00:19:18,750
我不知道  我不能让他死
I don't know. I'm not sending him home in a box.

423
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:23,230
我们得走了
We got to go.

424
00:19:23,240 --> 00:19:25,170
加布里尔的心律不齐  越来越严重了
Gabriel's arrhythmia, it's gotten worse.

425
00:19:26,590 --> 00:19:27,720
你还没找到
You still haven't found it?

426
00:19:27,720 --> 00:19:29,900
我可以让普莱斯顿小姐来回答所有问题
I can get Ms. Preston to address any questions --

427
00:19:29,900 --> 00:19:31,890
她没有参加手术  你参加了
She wasn't in the surgery. You were.

428
00:19:32,080 --> 00:19:35,270
她负责所有的医疗事故
She is the point person for all therapeutic misadventures.

429
00:19:35,270 --> 00:19:36,540
你在逗我吗
Are you kidding me?

430
