我可能会毫无理由失声
I may lose my voice for absolutely no reason,

431
00:19:40,970 --> 00:19:42,640
你却在用什么术语搪塞我
and you are using canned jargon.

432
00:19:42,640 --> 00:19:45,170
样杯里的不是牙膏
That sample cup doesn't have toothpaste

433
00:19:45,560 --> 00:19:47,170
袜子或者防晒霜  好吗
or socks or sunblock in it, okay?

434
00:19:47,170 --> 00:19:48,260
是我的命啊
It has my life!

435
00:19:53,490 --> 00:19:54,420
对不起
I'm sorry.

436
00:19:57,240 --> 00:19:58,110
谢谢
Thank you.

437
00:20:05,190 --> 00:20:07,590
-干得漂亮  -是啊
- Good for you. - Yeah, right.

438
00:20:07,590 --> 00:20:10,030
-我刚刚违反了大概八条规定  -也许吧
- I just broke about eight rules. - Maybe.

439
00:20:10,030 --> 00:20:12,040
我不会告诉「普莱斯顿小姐」的
"Ms. Preston" won't hear about it from me.

440
00:20:14,120 --> 00:20:16,000
不过你应该把样本找到
You should go find that sample, though.

441
00:20:17,420 --> 00:20:18,330
谢了
Thanks.

442
00:20:21,940 --> 00:20:24,690
药不起作用  为什么
The meds aren't working. The question is why.

443
00:20:25,740 --> 00:20:29,720
也许心律不齐只是
M-Maybe the arrhythmia is just another manifestation

444
00:20:29,720 --> 00:20:31,180
加布里尔机能障碍的另一个表现
of Gabriel's L.V. Dysfunction.

445
00:20:31,190 --> 00:20:34,510
我们至少还应该把这看成他异位的下降
We should still be seeing at least a modest decline in his ectopy.

446
00:20:34,510 --> 00:20:36,000
也许他的梯度变化曲线不太好
Maybe his gradient is worse.

447
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:37,700
我们可以试试钙通道阻滞剂
We could try calcium channel blockers.

448
00:20:37,700 --> 00:20:39,420
还有个更简单的解释
There's a much simpler explanation.

449
00:20:47,710 --> 00:20:50,150
关于他的心内膜炎有个好消息
Good news about his endocarditis --

450
00:20:50,150 --> 00:20:51,200
心脏炎症
heart inflammation.

451
00:20:51,200 --> 00:20:52,480
他的检查很正常
His tests are normal.

452
00:20:53,070 --> 00:20:54,730
但是我们还是很担心
But we still are concerned.

453
00:20:55,190 --> 00:20:57,830
出于某种原因  他的药没起作用
For some reason, his medication isn't helping.

454
00:20:58,470 --> 00:21:00,370
最好的解释就是...
Our best explanation is...

455
00:21:00,760 --> 00:21:03,290
他没有吃药
he hasn't been taking his medication.

456
00:21:18,280 --> 00:21:19,700
我是想救他的命
I am trying to save his life.

457
00:21:19,710 --> 00:21:20,890
通过不给他吃药吗
But withholding his medicine?

458
00:21:20,890 --> 00:21:22,530
通过把他留在这
By keeping him here.

459
00:21:23,450 --> 00:21:25,200
如果他吃了药  变好了
If he takes the medicine and becomes better,

460
00:21:25,200 --> 00:21:27,220
你是在送他去死
you send him to die.

461
00:21:27,420 --> 00:21:29,570
但是我们只能做到这了
But there is nothing else that we can do for him here.

462
00:21:29,570 --> 00:21:33,420
你不知道我生活的地方  那是什么样子
You do not understand where I live, what it is like.

463
00:21:34,950 --> 00:21:36,340
我不了解你的村子
I don't know your village.

464
00:21:37,880 --> 00:21:39,930
但是我知道穷是什么样的
But I do know what it's like to be poor.

465
00:21:41,450 --> 00:21:42,890
我小时候家里很穷
I grew up with nothing.

466
00:21:43,310 --> 00:21:44,480
我妹是残废
My sister was disabled.

467
00:21:44,480 --> 00:21:47,000
我父母负担不起她的药物和治疗
My parents couldn't afford her meds or treatments.

468
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:48,120
看着她痛苦
And it killed them,

469
00:21:48,790 --> 00:21:51,410
简直要了我父母和我的命
and me, to watch her suffer.

470
00:21:52,560 --> 00:21:56,240
但是当没有办法的时候  真的是无能为力了
But when nothing can be done, nothing can be done.

471
00:21:57,850 --> 00:21:59,510
你成为了一名医生
You became a doctor?

472
00:22:00,770 --> 00:22:03,380
你没有安于贫穷
You did not accept being poor.

473
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:06,010
不
No.

474
00:22:07,670 --> 00:22:10,050
那你一点都不了解
Then you do not understand at all.

475
00:22:13,190 --> 00:22:15,410
我们什么都没有  食物
We want for everything -- food.

476
00:22:16,240 --> 00:22:19,490
和平  药
Peace. Medicine.

477
00:22:20,960 --> 00:22:24,840
但是我们最想要的是希望
But our greatest want is hope.

478
00:22:27,530 --> 00:22:30,050
如果我们离开了  就没有希望了
If we leave here, we leave hope behind.

479
00:22:38,850 --> 00:22:39,820
好吧
Okay.

480
00:22:40,360 --> 00:22:41,580
我会尽力的
I'll do what I can.

481
00:22:47,110 --> 00:22:48,670
我来看一下伊丽莎白
I dropped by to see Elizabeth.

482
00:22:48,680 --> 00:22:50,560
毫不奇怪  她很沮丧
Not surprisingly, she's very upset.

483
00:22:50,560 --> 00:22:52,630
