There wasn't much I could offer in the way of comfort.

484
00:22:52,630 --> 00:22:54,270
要是人们都能各司其职就好了
If only people did their jobs.

485
00:22:54,510 --> 00:22:55,520
什么人
Which people?

486
00:22:56,130 --> 00:22:59,390
护士  送检员  化验室技术人员
Scrub nurses, couriers, lab techs...

487
00:22:59,390 --> 00:23:01,500
这真是个奇怪的清单
That's a curiously limited list.

488
00:23:01,510 --> 00:23:02,690
我的手术过程没有出错
I did the surgery correctly.

489
00:23:02,690 --> 00:23:03,820
同样  我不认为要求别人做好自己的
I don't think it's too much to expect others

490
00:23:03,820 --> 00:23:05,770
本职工作是一件过分的事情
to do their jobs correctly, as well.

491
00:23:05,820 --> 00:23:07,680
