So, not your fault, not your problem.

492
00:23:07,680 --> 00:23:09,500
你想做什么  让我觉得内疚吗
What are you trying to do, make me feel guilty?

493
00:23:09,500 --> 00:23:12,020
是的  我希望你感觉很糟糕
Yes. I want you to feel horrible.

494
00:23:12,030 --> 00:23:13,480
那是唯一会让你改变的事情
That's the only thing that's gonna make you change.

495
00:23:13,480 --> 00:23:15,430
-变成什么  -我嫁的那个人
- Into what? - The guy I married.

496
00:23:15,430 --> 00:23:18,580
那个关心病人大过于关心政治斗争的人
The guy who cared more about patients than politics.

497
00:23:18,920 --> 00:23:19,980
我懂了
Okay, I get it.

498
00:23:19,980 --> 00:23:22,780
你说的是我竞争医院院长的事情
This is about me vying for president of the hospital.

499
00:23:22,910 --> 00:23:24,390
我们已经详细讨论过了
Which we discussed at length,

500
00:23:24,390 --> 00:23:27,230
你也说你会百分之百支持我
which you said you were 100% behind me on.

501
00:23:27,230 --> 00:23:28,980
我没意识到我落后你多远了
I didn't realize how far behind.

502
00:23:29,210 --> 00:23:30,780
你认为我把你抛在身后了吗
You think I've left you behind?

503
00:23:34,240 --> 00:23:35,130
周二
Tuesday --

504
